            <p><span>The benefits of PPC and the various modalities of its engagement were presented in the APC&rsquo;s Green Paper on Effective Public-Philanthropic Collaboration in ASEAN.&nbsp; In sharing its main findings, Laurence Lien, CEO of APC, iterated that a mindset shift was critical in helping philanthropists and governments understand each other&rsquo;s relative strengths and unique context in addressing increasingly complex social problems.</span></p>
